DESCRIPTION:This post contains affiliate links. We may earn a commission at
	 no extra cost to you. \n\n  \n     Official Tickets\n   \n  \n     Resale
	 Tickets\n  \n\nComedy Cellar Las Vegas brings one of the most legendary n
	ames in stand-up comedy to the heart of Las Vegas. Located inside the Rio 
	Hotel & Casino\, this intimate comedy club is the West Coast home of New Y
	ork City’s world-famous Comedy Cellar\, the venue that helped launch the c
	areers of comedy icons including Dave Chappelle\, Chris Rock\, Jon Stewart
	\, Ray Romano\, Amy Schumer\, Aziz Ansari\, and countless others. \nUnlike
	 traditional comedy shows featuring a single headliner\, Comedy Cellar pre
	sents a carefully curated lineup of professional comedians every night. Au
	diences can expect multiple performers during each show\, featuring a mix 
	of nationally touring headliners\, television favorites\, Comedy Central v
	eterans\, Netflix performers\, and rising stars from around the world. \nN
	o two shows are exactly alike\, making every visit a unique experience. Su
	rprise drop-in appearances from major comedians performing elsewhere in La
	s Vegas have become part of the club’s reputation\, giving audiences the c
	hance to see comedy superstars in an intimate setting. \nEvent Details\nVe
	nue: Comedy Cellar Las Vegas at Rio Hotel & Casino\nLocation: 3700 W Flami
	ngo Rd\, Las Vegas\, NV 89103\nShow Schedule: Nightly performances through
	out the year\nAge Requirement: Recommended for audiences 18+ due to mature
	 comedy content \nAbout the Venue\nOpened in 2018\, Comedy Cellar Las Vega
	s was designed to recreate the atmosphere and energy of the original Green
	wich Village club that has become one of the most respected comedy venues 
	in the world. The 300-seat showroom offers excellent sightlines and an int
	imate setting that allows audiences to experience stand-up comedy exactly 
	as it was meant to be seen: up close and personal. \nThe venue combines th
	e excitement of a Las Vegas night out with the authentic feel of a classic
	 New York comedy club. Guests can enjoy a comfortable showroom environment
	 while watching some of the best comedians working today perform in a sett
	ing that encourages spontaneity\, crowd interaction\, and unforgettable mo
	ments. \nConveniently located inside the Rio Hotel & Casino just minutes f
	rom the Las Vegas Strip\, the venue offers easy access for both tourists a
	nd local comedy fans. \nWhat to Expect\nExpect a fast-paced evening featur
	ing multiple comedians performing throughout the show. The Comedy Cellar i
	s known for showcasing a wide variety of comedic styles\, from observation
	al humor and storytelling to sharp social commentary\, crowd work\, and cu
	tting-edge stand-up. \nWhether you’re discovering a future comedy star or 
	watching a seasoned veteran perfect their craft\, every show delivers the 
	authentic comedy club experience that has made the Comedy Cellar one of th
	e most respected brands in stand-up comedy. \nFor comedy fans visiting Las
	 Vegas\, Comedy Cellar is widely considered one of the best places in the 
	city to experience live stand-up comedy any night of the week.\n\nhttps://
	comedycalendar.com/event/comedy-cellar-las-vegas-showcase-early/2026-07-01
	/\n\nFrom Comedy Calendar
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/comedy-cellar-las-vegas-showcase-early
	/2026-07-01/
