	ervice with cocktails\, beer\, and wine available\nA fun\, festive atmosph
	ere to celebrate the holiday weekend\nDoors open 1 hour before showtime — 
	arrive early for the best seats\n\nVenue Information\nPunch Line Philly is
	 Philadelphia’s premier stand-up comedy club\, located at 33 E. Laurel Str
	eet in the heart of the city. The intimate showroom offers excellent sight
	lines from every seat\, and the Callback Bar opens 1 hour before showtime 
	for pre-show drinks and mingling. Parking lots are available behind the ve
	nue at 49 Richmond Street and 1025 N. Front Street. \nTicket Information\n
	Tickets for 50 First Jokes About America at Punch Line Philly are availabl
	e now. Resale tickets start at $44. There is an 8-ticket limit per person.
	 Tickets are non-refundable unless the event is cancelled or postponed. \n
