SUMMARY:Benji Brown LIVE at Arlington Improv (Sunday Show)
DTSTAMP:20260701T033033Z
DTSTART:20260705T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Official TicketsResale Tickets \nThis post contains affiliate l
	inks. We may earn a commission at no extra cost to you. \nAbout the Perfor
	mer\nBenji Brown is an urban comedian setting a new standard in comedy. He
	 toured with Martin Lawrence’s 2018 LIT AF Tour in major arenas across the
	 country and is now the host of Martin Lawrence’s “Yall Know What It Is To
	ur.” He headlined his own “Act Crazy If You Want To” national tour in 2019
	\, making him one of the only urban comedians — alongside Kevin Hart — wit
	h the clout to pull off a solo national tour of that magnitude. \nHis vira
	l character KiKi has garnered over 3 million views\, cementing him as one 
	of the next major urban comedic household names. \nEvent Details\nDate: Su
	nday\, July 5\, 2026 \nTime: 7:00 PM (Doors open 6:00 PM) \nVenue: Arlingt
	on Improv\, 309 Curtis Mathes Way #147\, Arlington\, TX 76018 \nAge Restri
	ction: 18+ \nPrice Range: $20 to $60 per person \nAbout the Venue\nArlingt
	on Improv is located in the Highlands Shopping Center in Arlington\, TX\, 
	across from Torchy’s Tacos. It is an intimate comedy club featuring a full
	 bar and restaurant where guests enjoy world-renowned and local comics in 
	a lively\, up-close setting. \nThe venue also hosts Black Dog Pizza Arcade
	\, a full-scale free-play retro arcade featuring more than 30 local craft 
	beers. Seating is assigned based on date of purchase. A 2-item food or bev
	erage minimum per person applies once seated\, and there is an 18% service
	 charge on all checks in the showroom. \nWhat to Expect\nBenji Brown close
	s out his Arlington Improv weekend run with a full Sunday headlining set. 
	Expect his signature urban humor\, viral character work\, and high-energy 
	delivery — the perfect way to wrap up your holiday weekend. \nThis is an 1
	8+ event. Doors open at 6:00 PM. Food and beverage service ends approximat
	ely 45 minutes into the show. All sales are final\, no refunds or exchange
	s. \nTicket Information\nTickets range from $20 to $60 per person. Purchas
	e official tickets or find resale options below. \nOfficial TicketsResale 
	Tickets\n\nhttps://comedycalendar.com/event/benji-brown-live-at-arlington-
	improv-sunday/\n\nFrom Comedy Calendar
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/benji-brown-live-at-arlington-improv-s
	unday/
LOCATION:Arlington Improv\, 309 Curtis Mathes Way #147\, Arlington\, TX\, 7
	6018\, United States Of America
